OL,3,CParents outraged as canal path walking
OL,4,Croute is 'putting children at risk'
OL,6,FParents in a village in Oswestry in
OL,7,FShropshire have told ITV News Central
OL,8,Fthey're scared for their children who
OL,9,Fwill have to walk on a "seriously
OL,10,Fdangerous" towpath to and from school.
OL,12,FA free bus service in Weston Rhyn has
OL,13,Fbeen in service for nearly 40 years to
OL,14,Fget children from the village to the
OL,15,Fnearest secondary school, St Martin's.
OL,17,FBut from September, any new children
OL,18,Fjoining the school will not be allowed
OL,19,Fon the bus. Instead, they will have to
OL,20,Fwalk along a canal towpath to get to
OL,21,Fand from school.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773943560
OL,3,CParents outraged as canal path walking
OL,4,Croute is 'putting children at risk'
OL,6,FShropshire Council said they recently
OL,7,Fcommissioned a reassessment of the
OL,8,Fwalking routes between Weston Rhyn and
OL,9,FSt Martin's School. It found the
OL,10,Froadside route still remains
OL,11,Funsuitable, but an alternative route
OL,12,Fhad been found.
OL,14,FThey said it's "been identified which
OL,15,Fprovides an available walking route
OL,16,Ffor accompanied pupils in line with
OL,17,Four statutory duty."
OL,19,FBut the council has since reviewed the
OL,20,Fassessment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773943560
OL,3,CParents outraged as canal path walking
OL,4,Croute is 'putting children at risk'
OL,6,FAndy Hall, Shropshire Council's
OL,7,FCabinet member for children and
OL,8,Feducation, said: "We understand the
OL,9,Fconcerns that have been raised. In
OL,10,Flight of this, we will reconsider the
OL,11,Fassessment to ensure the approach we
OL,12,Ftake is safe and all risks are taken
OL,13,Finto consideration.
OL,15,F"We will also look at all other
OL,16,Fassessments carried out back in 2023
OL,17,Fto make sure they are safe too."
OL,19,FBut parents are far from happy.
OL,26,@pD@ROUwD@AOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773943560
OL,3,CParents outraged as canal path walking
OL,4,Croute is 'putting children at risk'
OL,6,FMother Natalie New used to use the bus
OL,7,Fherself. Now she has two children. One
OL,8,Fuses the bus, but her son Jake, who is
OL,9,Fin primary school, may not be able to
OL,10,Fuse the bus when he joins the
OL,11,Fsecondary school.
OL,13,FShe said: "It's not safe at all!",
OL,14,Fbefore adding: "It's very muddy. It's
OL,15,Fslippy, especially when you've had 30-
OL,16,F40 children walking along it."
OL,18,FShe continued: "It's unlit, so dark
OL,19,Fmornings, dark evenings, there's no
OL,20,Fbarrier.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773943560
OL,3,CParents outraged as canal path walking
OL,4,Croute is 'putting children at risk'
OL,6,F"And we all know what children are
OL,7,Flike, a bit of fun a bit of shoving,
OL,8,Fthere's nothing stopping one of these
OL,9,Fchildren falling into the canal."
OL,11,FThe bus takes ten minutes to get to
OL,12,Fthe school.
OL,14,FBut the walk along the Shropshire
OL,15,FCanal towpath can take more than an
OL,16,Fhour, depending on where your home is.
OL,18,FMother Steph Burke is worried about
OL,19,Fher daughter Pippa who will be joining
OL,20,Fthe school this September.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773943560
OL,3,CParents outraged as canal path walking
OL,4,Croute is 'putting children at risk'
OL,6,F"I honestly think it's outrageous that
OL,7,Fthe criteria they've used to assess
OL,8,Fthis is putting our children at an
OL,9,Fincreased risk.
OL,11,F"They do not consider personal safety
OL,12,Fin this assessment. They don't
OL,13,Fconsider the lack of lighting, CCTV,
OL,14,Fall the erosion on the edges of the
OL,15,Fpath.
OL,17,F"Somebody needs to be with them which
OL,18,Falso effects how we get this one to
OL,19,Fschool and who goes to school in the
OL,20,Fvillage and we have work commitments
OL,21,Fas well. It's difficult."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773943560
OL,3,CParents outraged as canal path walking
OL,4,Croute is 'putting children at risk'
OL,6,FSt Martins School has also urged the
OL,7,Fcouncil to review it's plan, saying
OL,8,Fthe route is not a highway, and so
OL,9,Fshouldn't be used by it's students.
OL,11,FAlison Pope, Headteacher at St
OL,12,FMartin's said: "While existing pupils
OL,13,Fwill retain transport until the end of
OL,14,FYear 11, the school believes the canal
OL,15,Ftowpath does not meet the legal
OL,16,Fdefinition of an 'available route'
OL,17,Funder national guidance, as it is not
OL,18,Fa highway, not a public right of way,
OL,19,Fand is not maintained by the Local
OL,20,FAuthority.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773943560
OL,3,CParents outraged as canal path walking
OL,4,Croute is 'putting children at risk'
OL,6,F"It is owned and controlled by the
OL,7,FCanal & River Trust and may be closed
OL,8,Fat any time."
OL,10,FMs Pope said: "The school is also
OL,11,Fconcerned about the safeguarding
OL,12,Fimplications of a daily route
OL,13,Falongside deep, unfenced water on a
OL,14,Fnarrow, unlit towpath, and about the
OL,15,Flack of transparency and public
OL,16,Fscrutiny surrounding the decision.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773943560
OL,3,CParents outraged as canal path walking
OL,4,Croute is 'putting children at risk'
OL,6,F"We were pleased to hear...that
OL,7,FHeather Kidd and the council are now
OL,8,Flooking to review this decision and
OL,9,Fwelcome the fact they have listened to
OL,10,Fcommunity opinion."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
